00:20:59.690 --> 00:21:01.110
And also, what's in a name?

00:21:01.110 --> 00:21:08.540
Well, Linda's maiden name was
Bocucci, changed in the 1940's

00:21:08.540 --> 00:21:10.730
to avoid discrimination.

00:21:10.730 --> 00:21:16.840
So I present to you -- I'm
going to present each presenter

00:21:16.840 --> 00:21:20.260
and then I will introduce
the other one afterwards.

00:21:20.260 --> 00:21:26.280
So I am going to present to
you Linda Boccucci Osborne.

